      <postamble>
      	<html:p>QVT Operational will produce maintenance releases to align with the Galileo SR releases, that includes the Eclipse Platform 2.0.1 and 2.0.2 releases. QVT Operational may produce interim maintenance releases in addition to these in order to satisfy clients requests.
<html:ul>
<html:li>September 25, 2009 - QVT Operational 2.0.1 maintenance release (Galileo Service Release 1)</html:li>
<html:li>February 26, 2010 - QVT Operational 2.0.2 maintenance release (Galileo Service Release 2)</html:li>
<html:li>A list of issues indicated for the 2.0.x maintenance stream can be found in bugzilla.</html:li></html:ul> 
      	</html:p>
      </postamble>
